actual uks general terms and conditions for investment services and its order execution policy investment services  general terms and conditions find below btg pactuals general terms and conditions for investment services pactual europe llp  investment services general tc mifid client categorisation important notices markets in financial instruments directive  order execution policy mifid requires btg pactual to put in place an order execution policy and to take all reasonable steps to obtain the best possible result either when executing orders or when receiving and transmitting orders for execution on behalf of its clients mifid order execution policy a nonexhaustive list of the execution venues used by btg pactual can be found here see our code of business principles  ethics the information in this website is subject to change without notice nothing in it should be interpreted as a solicitation to engage in any investment activity in any jurisdiction privacy policy mifid uk stewardship code terms of use site map terms and policies disclaimer nonbrazilian investor please read the following comments about information published in the website this document is published exclusively for the purpose of providing information and conferring transparency to the management carried out by btg pactual and it is not the offering memorandum of the funds and is not to be considered as an offer for the sale of shares of the funds or of any other security some of the funds are not listed on the cayman islands stock exchange and are accordingly prohibited from making an offering to the public in the cayman islands in some cases no registration statement has been filed with the united states securities and exchange commission or any state securities authority with respect to the offering of the funds shares not all the funds presented here have their shares registered under the united states securities act of  as amended this document is not destined to investors with residence in brazil the funds may not be offered sold redeemed or transferred in brazil the offer and sale of the funds shares in certain jurisdictions may be restricted by law before subscribing for the shares each prospective investor should i carefully read and retain the offering memorandum of the funds and the relevant supplement or annex in respect of the portfolio andor class of shares ii consult with hisherits own counsel and advisors as to all legal tax regulatory financial and related matters concerning an investment in the funds past performance does not guarantee future results btg pactual takes no responsibility for the accidental publication of incorrect information nor for investment decisions taken based on this material access to this document or use of the services or information provided herein is prohibited by any person or entity in any jurisdiction or country where such distribution or use would be contrary to local law rule or regulation btg pactual europe llp  united kingdom  duedil search for a company or director sign insign inproductteamscustomersplansaboutinternationalbloghelptalk to sales    product teams customers plans about contact duedil btg pactual europe llp gbactiverecent credit rating updatereportadd to listkey informationactivitynews  socialpeoplelocationsdirectorsownershipgroupdocumentsfinancialscredit riskturnover m gbp net assets m gbp return on capital employed   debt to capital   detailscompany namebtg pactual europe llpcompany numberoclegal entity identifiervispglythg source company typeotherincorporation date mar type of accounts filingfull accountslatest annual returns  mar  next annual returns due  mar  latest annual accounts  dec  next annual accounts due  sep  sic  — sic  — websitehttpwwwbtgpactualcomsocial mediaregistered addressberkeley square house berkeley squarelondonwj brunited kingdomtrading addresses and phone numbers find contact information in the locations tab go to locationsdescription btg pactual europe llp was founde