 sued in hong kong by exemployee bloomberg lp retrieved  january  jenkins based in london was served on a visit to hong kong the court heard   a b cuadros alex cristiane lucchesi  september  btg’s esteves drives ‘better than goldman’ rise in bank’s clout  bloomberg bloomberg lp retrieved  january  esteves has had runins with regulators in three separate cases since  brazil’s central bank and securities commission alleged pactual had illegally transferred profits to foreign funds to disguise gains and avoid taxes esteves and his partners received warnings in the first two incidents in the third he and another partner were ordered to pay a combined settlement of  reais  with pactual paying another  million reais the case closed in  without any admission of guilt   schmidt blake sabrina valle  june  arrest of ‘big fish’ odebrecht ups the stakes in petrobras probe  bloomberg business bloomberg lp retrieved  july  police detained odebrecht  years old and otavio azevedo of andrade gutierrez sa friday as part of a coordinated federal operation involving  police officers in four states the strike is the culmination of months of digging by investigators who were convinced that a scheme involving petrobras insiders and contractors to rakeoff vast sums from inflated construction and service contracts had to have the blessings of corporate higherups   schmidt blake sabrina valle odebrecht ceo wrote note to destroy email police say bloomberg lp retrieved  july  the head of brazilian conglomerate odebrecht sa wrote a note to lawyers with the phrase “destroy rigs email” while he was in jail police said wednesday drawing more attention to the most senior executive detained in a wideranging graft investigation marcelo odebrecht  wrote the message that was handed to lawyers and photocopied at the jail as part of a routine search according to a police statement the note also mentions “andré esteves” which is the name of the billionaire banker who is ceo of grupo btg pactual sa   kiern