ossen teil der schrotthypotheken kaufte die bei der ubs zu den  milliarden franken abschreibungen und letztlich zum eingreifen des staates führten   jenkins patrick exubs man’s key role in brazil bank financial times retrieved  january  like most of those who were ejected from their jobs during the financial crisis he swiftly disappeared from view   bray chad dan horch  july  generali sells swiss private bank to btg pactual for  billion the new york times retrieved  july  the italian insurer generali group said on monday that it had agreed to sell bsi a swiss private lender to the banking unit of btg pactual group of brazil for about  billion   shotter james  march  former ubs banker branson to head finma financial times retrieved  july  before working for finma mr branson held a number of senior positions at ubs including working as chief financial officer of its wealth management and swiss bank business he was also in charge of ubs’s japanese securities unit between  and  a period during which employees at the division were involved in attempts to manipulate libor as a result he faced calls to step down in  after ubs reached a sfrbn settlement with a number of regulators including finma over allegations that it had manipulated interbank rates on an “epic” scale   ubs announces senior management appointments ubs  september  retrieved  july  mark branson currently ubss chief communication officer will become ceo of ubs securities japan ltd succeeding simon bunce recently appointed global head of fixed income for ubss investment bank in his new role reporting to huw jenkins ceo investment bank and rory tapner chairman and ceo asia pacific mark branson will oversee the development of ubss investment bank in japan and coordinate ubs group activities in one of the worlds largest and most important financial services markets   a b dubas sebastien le futur patron de bsi et son passé interpellent le temps sa retrieved  july  le repreneur ou le sauveur se nommait btg pactua