alle  june  arrest of ‘big fish’ odebrecht ups the stakes in petrobras probe  bloomberg business bloomberg lp retrieved  july  police detained odebrecht  years old and otavio azevedo of andrade gutierrez sa friday as part of a coordinated federal operation involving  police officers in four states the strike is the culmination of months of digging by investigators who were convinced that a scheme involving petrobras insiders and contractors to rakeoff vast sums from inflated construction and service contracts had to have the blessings of corporate higherups   schmidt blake sabrina valle odebrecht ceo wrote note to destroy email police say bloomberg lp retrieved  july  the head of brazilian conglomerate odebrecht sa wrote a note to lawyers with the phrase “destroy rigs email” while he was in jail police said wednesday drawing more attention to the most senior executive detained in a wideranging graft investigation marcelo odebrecht  wrote the message that was handed to lawyers and photocopied at the jail as part of a routine search according to a police statement the note also mentions “andré esteves” which is the name of the billionaire banker who is ceo of grupo btg pactual sa   kiernan paul  june  moody’s warns about ratings of two brazilian companies after arrest of ceos the wall street journal retrieved  july    senior brazilian senator and billionaire ceo both arrested for corruption the guardian reuters  november  retrieved  november   wikimedia commons has media related to goldman sachs  at reuters  at btg pactual investor relations retrieved from httpsenwikipediaorgwindexphptitlebtgpactualoldid categories banks of brazilcompanies based in são paulocompanies listed on the são paulo stock exchangeinvestment bankshidden categories cs germanlanguage sources decs portugueselanguage sources ptpages using infobox company with unsupported parametersall articles with unsourced statementsarticles with unsourced statements from april  navigation menu personal tools not